# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# mc4 — hardened root .gitignore
# Single source of truth after flattening 01-SATEX-CORE into mc4.
# Defense-in-depth on credentials, runtime data, build artifacts, OS junk,
# and the workspace junk that accumulates from sessions.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Node / package managers
node_modules/
.npm/
.pnpm-store/
.yarn/

# Build outputs
out/
dist/
build/
.vite/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Test / coverage
coverage/
.nyc_output/
.vitest-cache/

# Environment & secrets — keep templates, block everything else
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.production
.env.development
*.local
!.env
!.env.local.example
!.env.example

# Credentials material (defense in depth — these live in Electron userData,
# but explicitly block in case userData ever lands in the tree)
alpaca-creds.bin
anthropic-key.bin
*-creds.bin
*-key.bin
credentials.json
secrets.json
service-account.json

# SQLite & runtime data
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
userData/
app-data/

# Logs
*.log
logs/
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Electron / packaging
release/
*.dmg
*.exe
*.msi
*.app
*.deb
*.rpm
*.AppImage
*.snap

# OS junk
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db:encryptable
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# IDE / editor (Obsidian's .obsidian/ stays untracked too — workspace-local)
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.swn
.history/
*.code-workspace

# Workspace junk (transient session artifacts)
.tmp/
tmp/
.cache/
*.tmp
*.temp
.tmp_*
*.mp4
*.mov
Recording *
Screenshot *
Untitled.base

# Archived cruft — kept on disk for reference, never committed
RUBBISH/

# Dropped reference material (not SATEX source) -- see the declined in-app
# agent-runtime directive; this is the jim-schwoebel/awesome_ai_agents README catalog.
90-REFERENCE/

# Obsidian vault config — workspace-local, never shared. The markdown notes in
# Vault/ stay tracked; the .obsidian/ app-config dir does not.
.obsidian/

# Claude Code workspace state (local agent state should not be committed)
.claude/sessions/
.claude/projects/
.claude/local/

# SATEX vault — machine-local runtime + app-written state, never shared:
#   Observer = continuous-observer checkpoints (one every ~10 min)
#   Sessions = session-close artifacts
#   Settings = app-persisted workspace layout + per-symbol subsecond prefs
Vault/Observer/
Vault/Sessions/
Vault/Settings/

# Superpowers brainstorming visual-companion mockups (transient design aids)
.superpowers/

# Vault runtime artifacts (nightly self-eval reports, session learnings) --
# generated data, untracked by design; the READMEs stay tracked.
Vault/Backtests/*
!Vault/Backtests/README.md
Vault/Learnings/*
!Vault/Learnings/README.md

# Agent PR-body scratch files
**/.pr-body-*.md
